name: Taylor Justine
text: My absolute favorite mexican restaurant in town. Very authentic, no menus, everything made fresh right where you can see them, no mexican american bs. It's not a very well known place but that adds to it's appeal. 5-star hidden gem.

name: yeyo guillen
text: Great food ever all authentic mexican food absolutely recommended to everyone..authentic comida mexicana se lo recomiendo a todos muy rica..

name: Guadalupe Martinez
text: Love going here because this is AUTHENTIC mexican food. Everything is home made and they cook right where you can see them. Now this is one those restraunts that look run down but definitely worth it. The tripe tacos are the bomb & menudo on the weekends is my favorite. The waitresses are super friendly & they do pickup as well.

name: Richard Cordsen
text: Delicious authentic Mexican flavor and style!

name: Julian Contreras
text: One of best authentic Mexican restaurants in Albertville, AL. The building is not the best but they have amazing authentic Mexican food. Highly recommend!

name: Joey Serna
text: Food is amazing but awful customer service. Do not try and call to order food they will just answer it then hang up time and time again

name: Danny
text: The food is good though a little pricey. But they always answer the phone and no one answers then leave it unhung so no one can place a to go order!

name: Sparla Petty
text: Delicious food, oh my gosh! Hot, fresh tacos, my husband and I got so full when we went in for lunch, very authentic, great experience! 10 out of 10

name: Jacob M
text: Delicious authentic Spanish food. Ordered 4 tacos and had to order 2 more because they were so good!

name: Matt Owen
text: Best AUTHENTIC Mexican food EVER.  Limited space and was kinda of a wait to get the food.  But WELL worth it, no doubt.  You gotta try it

name: kristy Lanning
text: Would have given 5 stars because the food is awesome but I have called on many, many occasions and very seldom get an answer. Would just eat there if I wanted to stay 30 to 40 mins... wrote this 7 months ago..went inside yesterday and will never go back..the food was great but the waitress was rude..not 1 word from her..left a tip against my will...poor service
